Class MeterRate

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.comm.mndot.MeterRate
public class MeterRate extends Object
A meter rate controls whether a ramp meter is metering or flashing. There are 6 metering rates and 2 flashing rates.
Author:
Douglas Lau
